Spain’s Rajoy Says ‘Wouldn’t Like’ to Cut Pensions

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-09-19T07:30:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/spain-s-rajoy-says-wouldn-t-like-to-cut-pensions.html
Opposition leader  Mariano Rajoy 
said he “wouldn’t like” to cut pensions as he pledged to
reduce “superfluous” spending if he wins an election on Nov.
20, as polls indicate he will.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
